pdf2html is an easy to use ruby extension for the pdftohtml program

It is used to convert pdf files into html

Platforms
This gem only works on linux and mac. I don't a compiled version of the pdftothml for windows. Adding such a file to the bin
directory will enable support for windows.

Installation

gem install pdf2html :git => git://github.com:puneetht/pdf2html.git


Usage

require 'pdf2html'

Pdf2Html::Pdf2Html.set_binary_path
Pdf2Html::Pdf2Html.pdf2html("pdffile.pdf","outputfile.html")
